timeline.bodyText:
I think these can be replaced by the following, avoiding the need for the test and synchronization (which is part of the reason for using the Singleton model).
    private static FileWrapper fileWrapperInstance = new FileWrapper();
    private static FileWrapper getFileWrapperInstance() {
        return fileWrapperInstance;
    }

